output:
Fix: Explicitly define imagePullPolicy: Always in the container spec or verify latest tag behavior.

Example:
{
  "apiVersion": "apps/v1",
  "kind": "Deployment",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "nginx-deployment"
  },
  "spec": {
    "replicas": 3,
    "selector": {
      "matchLabels": {
        "app": "nginx"
      }
    },
    "template": {
      "metadata": {
        "labels": {
          "app": "nginx"
        }
      },
      "spec": {
        "containers": [
          {
            "name": "nginx",
            "image": "nginx:latest",
            "ports": [
              {
                "containerPort": 80
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}

Fix: Ensure the selector matches the pod labels exactly (`app: nginx`).

Example:
{
  "apiVersion": "v1",
  "kind": "Service",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "nginx-service"
  },
  "spec": {
    "selector": {
      "app": "nginx"
    },
    "ports": [
      {
        "protocol": "TCP",
        "port": 80,
        "targetPort": 80
      }
    ],
    "type": "ClusterIP"
  }
}

Fix: Check if a matching PV exists or if dynamic provisioning is enabled (check StorageClass).

Example:
{
  "apiVersion": "v1",
